{"title_page": "Shafi Uddin Shafi", "text_new": "{{short description|Bangladeshi film director}}\n{{infobox person \n| name = Shafi Uddin Shafi\n| occupation = Film Director\n| nationality = [[Bangladesh]]i\n}}\n'''Shafi Uddin Shafi''' is a [[Bangladesh]]i film director. As of December 2019 he directed 24 films.<ref name=a/>\n\n==Biography==\nShafi's first direction ''Gaddari''. It was released in 2003.<ref name=a/> At the beginning of his career he directed films along with Iqbal. Later, he started directing films individually.<ref name=b/>\n\n==Selected filmography==\n* ''Gaddari''<ref name=a>{{cite web|url=http://www.m.mzamin.com/article.php?mzamin=202804|title=\u09b8\u09be\u09ab\u09bf\u09b0 \u2018\u09b8\u09bf\u0995\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u099f \u098f\u099c\u09c7\u09a8\u09cd\u099f\u2019-\u098f \u09ac\u09be\u09aa\u09cd\u09aa\u09c0 \u0993 \u0989\u09b7\u09cd\u09a3|date=8 December 2019|accessdate=8 January 2020|website=Manabzamin|language=bn\n}}</ref>\n* ''Tomar Jonyo Morte Pari''<ref name=b>{{cite web|url=https://m.risingbd.com/entertainment/news/116828/\u09b8\u09be\u09ab\u09bf-\u0989\u09a6\u09cd\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8-\u09b8\u09be\u09ab\u09bf\u09b0-\u099c\u09a8\u09cd\u09ae\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8\n|title=\u09b8\u09be\u09ab\u09bf \u0989\u09a6\u09cd\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8 \u09b8\u09be\u09ab\u09bf\u09b0 \u099c\u09a8\u09cd\u09ae\u09a6\u09bf\u09a8\n|date=22 July 2015|accessdate=8 January 2020|website=risingbd.com|language=bn\n}}</ref>\n* ''Prem Mane Na Badha''<ref name=b/>\n* ''Machineman''<ref name=a/>\n* ''Boro Vai Zindabad''<ref name=b/>\n* ''[[O Sathii Re|O Sathi Re]]''<ref name=a/>\n* ''Dhakar King''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.prothom-alo.com/detail/news/282150\n|title=\u0988\u09a6\u09c7 \u0986\u099f \u099b\u09ac\u09bf\n|date=16 August 2012|accessdate=8 January 2020|website=Prothom Alo|language=bn\n}}</ref>\n* ''[[Prem Prem Paglami]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://m.prothomalo.com/entertainment/article/12014/\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u09ae-\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09c7\u09ae-\u09aa\u09b